{"tid":2443784,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港龍航空創辦人曹光彪逝世 享年101歲","createTime":"2021-03-12T09:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T15:13:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4622940ec1a4f13c34b15cd91551d763ffac75b3","tid":2443784,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"《澎湃新聞》報道，曹光彪於3月12日凌晨在香港逝世，享年101歲，而報道引述消息為曹光彪親友。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，曹光彪祖籍寧波市鄞州區下應鎮曹隘村，1920年出生於上海。曹光彪生前任香港永新企業有限公司董事長、港龍航空有限公司董事會名譽主席、毛里求斯駐香港榮譽總領事等職。<br />\n<br />\n曹光彪最為人稱道的是創建港龍航空公司，結束了香港航空事業被外資壟斷的歷史。<br />\n<br />\n惟國泰（293）及太古 （019） 於1990年便從曹光彪手上收購了港龍航空35%股份，時稱中信泰富的 中信股份（267） 則收購了38%。2006年，國泰全面收購港龍航空。惟去年因武漢肺炎，港龍航空品牌被拋棄，隱沒於歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210312/SUGS63FSFJEWJBKXHRO3I5XHKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210312%2FSUGS63FSFJEWJBKXHRO3I5XHKA%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=847ef4e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210312%2FSUGS63FSFJEWJBKXHRO3I5XHKA%2F&h=96225800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210312/SUGS63FSFJEWJBKXHRO3I5XHKA/</a>"},{"pid":"8a9fc937a32c03608b3ea9ce78a7fb6dd59ece1b","tid":2443784,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb0d9bcbf42ee1522405183ae02256fcc776ffe","tid":2443784,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"RIP"}]}